collections.name: Midnight Whiskers
collections.description:
Midnight Whiskers is a sleek black cat with glowing yellow eyes, sitting in a relaxed yet alert position. His dark fur creates a striking contrast against his brilliant golden eyes, giving him an air of mystery and charm. He sports a bold red hat that adds a touch of personality and flair to his appearance. With his body slightly turned to the side and his tail curled gracefully, he exudes calm confidence.
Fun Fact: Did you know? Midnight Whiskers is said to bring good luck to those who spot him under a full moon! 🌕✨ This rare and enchanting feline is more than just a pixel art masterpiece—he’s the guardian of secrets and whispers of the night.
